            <h1>Blood Donation Requirements</h1>
            <p id="p1">
              You may be wondering if you can donate blood. Donating blood is
              safe and easy to do, but there are a few basic requirements to
              donate blood.
            </p>

            <p id="p2">
              <strong>Why are there requirements to donate blood?</strong>
              Eligibility requirements are important to help ensure the safety
              of both the blood donor and blood recipient.
            </p>

            <p id="p3">
              Blood donations save lives every day, and donors are needed every
              day.<u
                ><b
                  >About 62 percent of the U.S. population is eligible to donate
                  at any one time but only 3 percent do so</b
                ></u
              >.
            </p>
