      <div class="main">
        <div class="BasicRequirements">
          <h2>Requirements & Recommendations</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Must be at least 16 years old</li>
            <li>Weigh at least 110 pounds</li>
            <li>Be in good general health</li>
            <li>Bring your ID</li>
            <li>Eat within 2 hours ahead of your donation</li>
            <li>Drink plenty of non-alcoholic liquids</li>
            <li>Wait eight weeks between whole blood donations</li>
          </ul>
